title: Leandro e Leonardo - Vol 6
description:
Leandro and Leonardo, born in Goianapolis, formed a double Brazilian. They have done very successfully in the 90s until June 23 in 1998 Leandro victim died of cancer. The double was the most successful in Brazil with more than 20 million copies sold and 12 CDs released by the end of the double in 1998. Leonardo, even saddened by the loss, continued in solo career with much success so far.
